en: It is really nice how Jirka and Frid are getting along so well so soon after they got together.
cz: Je to velmi pěkné jak se Jirka a Frid k sobě mají a jak dobře jim to jde.

en: ...yeah, yeah... I guess it is nice between them... but I think it is not exactly how it should be.
cz: ...ano, ano... asi je to pěkné mezi nimi... ale nemyslím si že je to tak jak by mělo být.
